nn_library.topologies.TEST_TOPOLOGY(input_shape, num_of_classes)

Function that initializes ANN (Artificial Neural Network) model using TEST_TOPOLOGY. Multidimensional input (image in numpy array type) is converted to one dimension. Only hidden dense layers.

Parameters

  • input_shape – input shape for the model

  • num_of_classes – number of output classes for the model

Returns

ANN model
